channel.title: UEA hockey photos
channel.description: Once upon a time I played hockey for the University of East Anglia while I was doing my PhD there, and a bit after that. We typically drank too much and as a result weren’t as good at hockey as we could have been, but still... it‘s having fun that counts, right? I brought the Team Toilet man of the match punishment idea from UMIST where it studied before UEA. Similar themes have been kept up the the Mutineers touring side with many trips to Weymouth at easter. There have even been some weddings. Some folks have their own webpages, which I could link here (hint). If you ever played bunnies, or wanted to brush up on the rules, then against all the rules of the noble order of the buffalo, here they are: Bunnies
